G A M E - P L O T
-------------------------------------
A remake of the first Resident Evil 
game with the DS's unique feature set 
in mind as you work your way through 
the now classic storyline involving 
Jill Valentine, Chris Redfield and that 
well-known mansion that introduced the 
world to Resident Evil back in 1996. 
Zombies are now smarter and actually 
work their way around doors as they 
chase after you. You'll find that 
there's no solace in a room that you 
think you've completely freed from 
zombie infestation.
